description: Home of the original hog dog, The Twisted Texan is bringing a terrific twist on the old-fashioned hot dog! Comfort food with a great attitude, every bite from this down-home delight of a truck is sure to brighten your day with fantastic flavor. With their original hog dogs, bacon wrapped hot dogs, Texas-sized sliders and more, The Twisted Texan is sure to have something to satisfy your cravings!
name: The Twisted Texan
